revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Categories go at the bottom of this page and interwikis go in Wikidata. -->
{{tsh|sp?}}

== Usage ==
:{{tlx|verify spelling|2=reason=text to replace default message on mouseover|3=date={{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}|4=pre-text=text to be displayed before the text in the reason parameter|5=post-text=text to be displayed after the text in the reason parameter}}

This should be used in articles where the correctness of a word, term or phrase's spelling or rendering is unknown. See also {{tl|clarify}} for other text that is difficult to understand. This template is a self-reference and so is part of the Wikipedia project rather than the encyclopedic content.

== Tracking categories ==
* {{clc|Wikipedia articles needing clarification}}

==TemplateData==
{{TemplateDataHeader}}
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"reason": {
			"label": "mouseover text",
			"description": "explanation of why spelling must be verified",
			"example": "spelling not attested in sources cited",
			"type": "line",
			"autovalue": "Please check the spelling/rendering of the word, term or phrase preceding this tag."
		},
		"date": {
			"label": "month and year",
			"description": "the month and year the tag was added",
			"example": "March 2018",
			"type": "date",
			"default": "May 2025",
			"autovalue": "May 2025",
			"suggested": true
		}
	},
	"format": "inline",
	"description": "This should be used in articles where the correctness of a word, term or phrase's spelling or rendering is unknown."
}
</templatedata>

==See also==
* {{tl|Typo help inline}}
